''See also [[declaré]], [[déclaré]]''
==English==

===Verb===
{{en-infl-reg-other-e|declar|e}}
# {{intransitive}}: To make a [[declaration]].
# {{intransitive}}: To [[announce]] one’s [[support]], [[choice]], [[opinion]], etc.
# {{intransitive}}, {{cricket}}: For the [[captain]] of the batting side to announce the [[innings]] [[complete]] even though all [[batsman|batsmen]] have not been [[dismiss]]ed.
# {{transitive}}: To announce something [[formal]]ly or [[official]]ly.
# {{transitive}}: To [[affirm]] or [[state]] something [[emphatic]]ally.
# {{transitive}}, {{cricket}}: To declare (an innings) closed.

